<paragraph blockId="31.[264,1323,1793,1899]" box="[264,366,1793,1818]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">
<emphasis box="[264,366,1793,1818]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">Remarks</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="31.[264,1323,1793,1899]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">
Bowman (1973) recognised six species, one of which he described as new. One additional species has been described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Zeidler, W." box="[695,884,1873,1899]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32" pagination="1383 - 1396" refId="ref31684" refString="Zeidler, W. (1992 b) A new species of amphipod of the genus Lestrigonus (Crustacea: Amphipoda: Hyperiidea: Hyperiidae) from eastern Australia. Journal of Plankton Research, 14 (10), 1383 - 1396." type="journal article" year="1992">Zeidler (1992b)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="32.[264,1323,284,630]" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">
Very little is known about the biology of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Milne-Edwards" authorityYear="1830" box="[792,930,284,309]" class="Malacostraca" family="Lestrigonidae" genus="Lestrigonus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="32" pageNumber="33" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[792,930,284,309]" italics="true" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">Lestrigonus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. All records of associations with gelatinous plankton have been with medusae (
<bibRefCitation author="Harbison, G. R. &amp; Biggs, D. C. &amp; Madin, L. P." box="[818,1068,324,350]" pageId="32" pageNumber="33" pagination="465 - 488" refId="ref26746" refString="Harbison, G. R., Biggs, D. C. &amp; Madin, L. P. (1977) The associations of Amphipoda Hyperiidea with gelatinous zooplankton - II. Associations with Cnidaria, Ctenophora and Radiolaria. Deep-Sea Research, 24, 465 - 488." type="journal article" year="1977">
Harbison 
<emphasis box="[937,991,324,349]" italics="true" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">et al</emphasis>
. 1977
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Laval, P." box="[1083,1222,324,350]" pageId="32" pageNumber="33" pagination="11 - 56" refId="ref27842" refString="Laval, P. (1980) Hyperiid amphipods as crustacean parasitoids associated with gelatinous plankton. Oceanography and Marine Biology, Annual Review, 18, 11 - 56." type="journal article" year="1980">Laval 1980</bibRefCitation>
). Additional biological information is given for 
<taxonomicName authority="(Stebbing 1888)" baseAuthorityName="Stebbing" baseAuthorityYear="1888" box="[789,1198,364,390]" class="Malacostraca" family="Lestrigonidae" genus="Lestrigonus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="32" pageNumber="33" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="schizogeneios">
<emphasis box="[789,988,364,389]" italics="true" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">L. schizogeneios</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Stebbing, T. R. R." box="[1011,1190,364,390]" pageId="32" pageNumber="33" pagination="1 - 1737" refId="ref30066" refString="Stebbing, T. R. R. (1888) Report on the Amphipoda collected by H. M. S. ' Challenger' during the years 1873 - 1876. Report on the Scientific Results of the Voyage of H. M. S. ' Challenger' during the years 1873 - 76 Zoology, 29, i - xxiv + 1 - 1737, pls 1 - 210." type="journal article" year="1888">Stebbing 1888</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Laval, P." pageId="32" pageNumber="33" pagination="25 - 67" refId="ref27629" refString="Laval, P. (1968 a) Developpement en elevage et systematique d' Hyperia schizogeneios Stebb. (Amphipode Hyperide). Archives de Zoologie Experimentale et Generale, 109 (1), 25 - 67." type="journal article" year="1968">Laval (1968a</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Laval, P." box="[360,423,404,430]" pageId="32" pageNumber="33" pagination="49 - 74" refId="ref27762" refString="Laval, P. (1972) Compartement, parasitisme et ecologie d' Hyperia schizogeneios Stebb. (Amphipode Hyperide) dans le plancton de Villefranche-Sur-Mer. Annales de l'Institut Oceanographique, Nouvelle Serie, 48, 49 - 74." type="journal article" year="1972">1972</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="32.[264,1323,284,630]" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">Distributional information for the species is provided by Bowman (1973), Bowman and McGuinness (1982) and Zeidler (1998).</paragraph>
